        "text": "But Pekah the son of Remaliah.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " Remaliah was probably a man of some importance, since Pekah seems to have been almost better known by his patronymic, Ben-Remaliah, \"son of Remaliah,\" than by his own proper name (see ",
        "children": []
      },
