      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", to be high) - certainly not the harem (Ewald), if Pekahiah was feasting there with his friends (",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "greek",
        "text": "δολοφονηθεὶς ἐν",
